28-29 August - Chocolate Satin Frosting

- 2   cup sifted confectioners sugar
- 1/4 cup soft butter
- 1   tablespoon milk
- 1   teaspoon vanilla
- 1/8 teaspoon salt
- 1   egg
- 2   oz Nestle's choco-bake (editor's note: this doesn't exist anymore, but you can use 6 tablespoons cocoa powder and 2 tablespoon shortening instead)

Combine in bowl and beat until well blended. Fills and frosts 2 8" r 9" cake layers or 24 cupcakes. 
